%N A077246 Bisection (even part) of Chebyshev sequence with Diophantine property.
%C A077246 3*a(n)^2 - 5*b(n)^2 = 7, with the companion sequence b(n)= A077245(n).
%C A077246 The odd part is A077244(n) with Diophantine companion A077243(n).
%H A077246 Tanya Khovanova, <a href="http://www.tanyakhovanova.com/RecursiveSequences/RecursiveSequences.html">Recursive Sequences</a>
